  <p>
    I even won an award (you can probably find it on my LinkedIn). I worked on some really cool projects—but over time, it started feeling repetitive. Same kind of work, same routine. That’s when I knew I needed to evolve again.
  </p>

  <p>
    Outside of all this, I’ve always loved anime—One Piece and Naruto are my favorites. I read manga too. And I genuinely enjoy meeting new people and hearing their stories.
  </p>

  <p>
    Recently, I met some amazing people at a tech meetup—it reminded me how important real connections are:
  </p>

